    "body": "Related: https://github.com/atom/electron/issues/3943.\n\nI think that @paulcbetts suggested this [here](https://github.com/atom/electron/issues/3921#issuecomment-167716088) and @zcbenz appeared to concur [here](https://github.com/atom/electron/issues/3921#issuecomment-167721369).\n"
