    "created_at": "2016-01-08T04:31:53Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-01-08T04:31:53Z",
    "body": "Imo window.open should inherit properties of the parent as well (like icon etc). \n\nFrom a security perspective though, you might get a false sense of security. Electron doesn't have Chromes sandbox and there might be inadvertent ways into the node code even with node integration off.  E. G.  That icon I mentioned allows a remote page to get node to load a file from the file system. \n"
  },
